  "title": "HR Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Assist with the maintenance and updating of employee personal records.</li>\n  <li>Manage employee leave and track attendance.</li>\n  <li>Support the maintenance of training records and monitor training progress.</li>\n  <li>Perform other HR-related duties as assigned by the HR Department.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office, especially Excel and Word.</li>\n  <li>Hold a Diploma in Human Resource Management or a related field.</li>\n  <li>Possess 1–2 years of experience in HR and administrative roles.</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in the construction industry is an added advantage; training will be provided.</li>\n</ul>",
